<MainLayout title="Mountain Experience">

<h1>Mountain Experience</h1>

<p>
Join us for an authentic rural adventure in Željezno Polje near the beautiful
mountain area of Mahnjača.
</p>

<h2>What you will experience</h2>

<ul>
<li>Hiking through beautiful mountain landscapes</li>
<li>Tractor ride with a trailer to the mountain</li>
<li>Fresh mountain spring water</li>
<li>Organic raspberries and blackberries</li>
<li>Traditional Bosnian lunch</li>
<li>Cooking Bosnian potato pie under the sač</li>
</ul>

<h2>Traditional Cooking Experience</h2>

<p>
Visitors can participate in preparing traditional Bosnian potato pie
(krompiruša). The pie is baked under the <strong>sač</strong>, a traditional
metal lid covered with hot coals. Guests can help prepare the dough,
fill the pie with mountain-grown potatoes, and enjoy the meal together.
</p>

<h2>Nature and Relaxation</h2>

<p>
The experience takes place in the peaceful mountain environment of
Željezno Polje, surrounded by forests, fresh air, and beautiful views.
</p>

<a href="/contact" class="btn">Book This Experience</a>

